<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/favicon.ico">
  <title>Challan</title>
  <style>
  @font-face {
    font-family: Metropolis-Regular;
    src: url(fonts/Metropolis-Regular.otf);
  }
  @font-face {
    font-family: Metropolis-Bold;
    src: url(fonts/Metropolis-Bold.otf);
  }
  body,
      table,
      td,
      a {
        text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #FFFFFF;
        color: #000000;
      }
      table {
        display: table;
        border-collapse: separate;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-indent: initial;
        unicode-bidi: isolate;
        border-spacing: 1px;
        border-color: gray;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="font-family: arial;font-size: 15px;line-height: normal;font-weight: normal;">
  <div class="mainbox" style="max-width: 700px; width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div class="width100" style="float: left;width: 100%;border: 1px solid #2C347F;margin: 15px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row" style="">
            <div style="padding: 0px 20px;border-top: 20px solid #2C347F; border-bottom: 2px solid #2C347F" class="col-lg-12">
                <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/logo.png" style="max-height: 100px;" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="padding: 20px;background-color: #FFFFFF;">
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Hello <%= user_name %>!</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Welcome to the QuicKart family!</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">We're thrilled to have you on board & excited to deliver fresh products right to your doorstep daily.</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">At QuicKart, we believe in the power of fresh, high-quality products. From our farm-fresh dairy, including creamy milk, paneer & yogurt, to our seasonal fruits & vegetables, every item is carefully selected to ensure you get the best of nature's bounty.</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Here's what you can expect as a QuicKart customer:</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
                <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/farm_fresh.png" alt="Farm Fresh Dairy" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 5px;">
                <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/fresh_produce.png" alt="Fresh Produce" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/order.png" alt="one time order" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="get_start_btn" style="background-color: #218d44;color: #FFF;font-weight: bold;margin: 10px 0 25px 0;display: inline-block;border-radius: 20px;padding: 5px 10px;">How to Get Started:</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="work_list" style="display:flex; align-items:center;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <div class="work_img" style="margin-right: 10px;">
                        <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/range.png" alt="Explore Our range" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 40px;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="work_text"><span style="color:#2d347f;font-weight: bold;">Explore Our Range :</span>Visit our website or app to browse our selection of farm-fresh products.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="work_list" style="display:flex; align-items:center;margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    <div class="work_img" style="margin-right: 10px;">
                        <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/your_order.png" alt="Customize Your Order" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 40px;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="work_text"><span style="color:#2d347f;font-weight: bold;">Customize Your Order :</span>Choose your preferred delivery slots and set up subscriptions for hassle-free regular deliveries.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="work_list" style="display:flex; align-items:center;margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <div class="work_img" style="margin-right: 10px;">
                        <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/freshness.png" alt="Enjoy Freshness Every Day" class="img-fluid" style="max-width: 40px;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="work_text"><span style="color:#2d347f;font-weight: bold;">Enjoy Freshness Every Day :</span>Sit back and relax as we bring the freshest products right to your doorstep.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">We're here to make your experience delightful and easy. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our friendly customer support team.</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Thank you for choosing QuicKart. We look forward to serving you with the freshest, highest-quality products for years to come!</div>
            <div class="col-lg-12" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Happy Shopping!<br>Sincerely, Team QuicKart</div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12" style="text-align: center; background-color: #F7F7F7; position: relative;">
            <div class="foote_socialicon">
              <table style="width: 100%;">
                <tbody>
                  <tr style="vertical-align: bottom;">
                    <td>
                      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/QuicKart.uae" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/facebook.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                      <a href="https://twitter.com/Quickartuae/" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/twitter.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/quickartuae/" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/instagram.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/quickart-general-trading-llc/" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/linkeding.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@quickartuae7767" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/youtube.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                      <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.quickart.customer&pli=1" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/googleplay.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/in/app/quickart/id1624846848" target="_blank"><img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/appstore.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 30px;"></a>
                    </td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                      <a href="#" class="qrcode">
                        <img src="<%= baseurl %>/images/mail_logo/qrcode.png" class="img-fluid" style="max-height: 100px;">
                      </a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">

        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12" style="border-bottom: 20px solid #2C347F;margin: 10px 0 0 0;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>